  "slug": "grief-support-and-the-impact-of-death-on-society",
  "title": "All-Party Parliamentary Group on Grief Support and the Impact of Death on Society",
  "purpose": "To bring together bereavement services, charities, faith communities, health professionals, public sector organisations, and bereaved individuals to: raise awareness across Parliament of the impact of bereavement on adults and children; recognise grief support as a public health issue; and campaign for change for the wellbeing of bereaved people across the UK.",
